Package: blockr.ggplot
Title: Interactive ggplot2 Charts for Blockr
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Nicolas", "Bennett", , "nicolas@cynkra.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Christoph", "Sax", , "christoph@cynkra.com", role = "aut")
  )
Description: Provides comprehensive blocks for plotting with blockr using
    'ggplot2'.  Includes PowerBI-style chart types (bar charts, line
    charts, pie charts, scatter plots) as well as statistical plots
    (boxplots, histograms, density plots, violin plots, heatmaps) with
    rich customization options and intuitive user interfaces.
